Description: Limestone ostracon bearing Coptic text contaning the Anaphora.
Excavator/field collector: Excavated by: Henri Édouard Naville (1893-94, on behalf of EEF)
Curator's comments: EA 32799 + EA 33050 Written in the same hand as O.Crum 4 & 6. O.Crum 4+7, H. Quecke, Or.Chr.Per. 37 (1971) 391-405. Studied with a view to publication by Mihálykó, 2021.
